                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Should the state hold an editorial convention? It would provide for the
                    creation of a code of ethics, generally improve the quality of
                newspapers</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>On the whole, Mr. Letcher evinces a spirit of compromise and patriotism
                    highly creditable to him....</excerpt>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Review of Rep Letcher's recent speech. Spectator supports him, agrees that
                    tariff needs revision, sections should try to get along</summary>
